metadata.name: The Tower
metadata.description:
Landscape #6

Built after the great war of the second age, this serves as the resting ground for the kings elite knights, men who've lead to countless victories, claiming victory to lands as far as the eyes can see. That great age has passed now, and what remains are but figments of a long forgotten time.

Created By Calder Moore
C4D, Octane, Photoshop
2250x3000px
1/1
